Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当月光照射黑暗的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.57,0:00:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说在宇宙飞舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.30,0:00:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展开决斗之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.44,0:00:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡的呼声远远的传开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.02,0:00:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.96,0:00:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪恶为此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.80,0:00:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换取持续戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.87,0:00:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为命运而不知所措之\N叹息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.24,0:00:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因无法抹去的记忆\N而为爱颤抖着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当月光照亮黑夜之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.19,0:01:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说促使得宇宙舞动着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.16,0:01:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的坠天使们啊\N美丽的飞翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.23,0:01:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的决斗展开时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.97,0:01:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遥远的地方呼喊着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.49,0:01:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四话塔中的小公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸...问你唷、问你唷，爱娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.97,0:01:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次来到城堡的英司少爷\N他如何啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.47,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是还是一样很困惑啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.17,0:01:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，不过我觉得他很努力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了找他姊姊才来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.95,0:01:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让人觉得好感动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我的母性本能油然而生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.98,0:02:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，他老爱鎌东鎌西的\N有够难伺候耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.06,0:02:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布丽姬妲，不可以这样子\N说你负责的服务对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.83,0:02:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是~这是事实啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.67,0:02:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到惩罚了吧，布丽姬妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.71,0:02:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来斗牙少爷跟英司少爷\N一样都是17岁耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.31,0:02:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过完全不同型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.34,0:02:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷从小就没有出过城外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.68,0:02:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个"纯粹培养"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘伊露，晚上要小声一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.89,0:02:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷跟英司少爷\N爱娜你喜欢哪一个?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.96,0:02:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.09,0:02:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜脑子里\N只有斗牙少爷一个人嘛~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.26,0:02:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事，人家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.74,0:03:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.55,0:03:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该...不是其他女仆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊~~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安全带检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血压脑波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,测定装置检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就位，OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G电位、身体提升装置启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温柔点，再温柔点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话， 就不叫做训练了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫香也做过这种事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爷，没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文好像真的要磨练他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.72,0:04:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂...我跟你有仇啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你要驾驶神机超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少得要轻松完成\N这种程度的训练才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK，斗牙\N结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一次不错的训练呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷，辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.98,0:04:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊斗牙，又创新纪录了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.79,0:04:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问你喔、问你喔，斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么样才能做到这么好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我一点诀窍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诀窍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.10,0:05:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没做什么特别的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，让我再试一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不稍微休息一下是办不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说做就做!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也好，进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司真是可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会那么直肠子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.12,0:05:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司干嘛生气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.39,0:05:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用在意没关系的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.69,0:05:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过他还真是个顽固的孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，昨晚要回寝室的途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个白影突然飘过眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.27,0:05:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追过去一看\N却根本没半个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道不会是窗帘吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.81,0:05:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝对没有看错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.17,0:05:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝶雪拉跟裘伊露\N还有玛莉妮雅也都看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而更难以置信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.88,0:05:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这座城堡里会出现幽灵\N的确也没什么好奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.75,0:05:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌，别说得这么可怕嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵比外星异种强吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.96,0:06:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊\N就是因为从小就接受战斗训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就变成\N四肢发达头脑简单了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.73,0:06:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多学一点常识嘛，常识!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.27,0:06:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轮不到你来说!\N好痛哦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵...\N耳朵?耳朵怎样了?...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫香?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.58,0:06:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，搞不好那个像幽灵般\N的影子就是绫香本人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正又没到西塔的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.15,0:06:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向女仆们打听\N也没有人知道绫香的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.76,0:06:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手上又只有这一点点情报而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，为什么会找我一起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.93,0:06:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人的话\N搞不好又会迷路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我，绫香是个怎么样的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.71,0:06:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有兄弟姊妹和家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不知道有个姊姊\N会是什么滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们很要好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.29,0:07:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小时候我父母就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.40,0:07:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来我们姊弟就相依为命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很温柔、又漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.77,0:07:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脑筋虽好却有点迟钝\N而且又爱哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.24,0:07:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本应该只是个普通上班女郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然却换了工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我联络说要到\N什么城里去工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.98,0:07:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以短时间内不会回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在我开始担心的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.78,0:07:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然收到一封她寄来的求救信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察又靠不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.59,0:07:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到处打听之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.36,0:07:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才终于来到这座城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽..幽灵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是雪貂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这种地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，等等我一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是通到哪儿去啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.39,0:08:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里好像是南塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南塔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.29,0:08:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经听爱娜提过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.90,0:09:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这座城堡有东、西、\N南、北、及中央五座城塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.40,0:09:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有桑德曼的允许\N绝对不可以进入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在女仆间好像也流传着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.11,0:09:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“每一个塔都藏有着\N各自的秘密”这样的流言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五座塔以及五个秘密啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.92,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来，绫香也是失踪于西塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.42,0:09:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.77,0:09:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗罗多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是绫香吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.89,0:09:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说...你是女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一看就知道了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.36,0:10:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.24,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会说话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好的回答我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.11,0:10:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司虽然动不动就生气\N不过他是个很体贴的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又没在生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧，又生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是斗牙，你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.66,0:10:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.83,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它见到你好像很高兴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.30,0:10:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为它迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.97,0:10:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷路?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.97,0:10:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.41,0:10:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊...是为了找它\N所以才半夜出来到处跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.50,0:11:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙，怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.23,0:11:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们会被骂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.15,0:11:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事情吗，叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.88,0:11:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这么晚了\N你的灯还亮着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以过来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.89,0:11:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.76,0:11:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过罗罗多已经回来了\N所以就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N让你做了这么不情愿的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有其他G因子拥有者的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.27,0:11:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也就不用去驾驶G战影了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.69,0:12:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出击了!莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗罗多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.97,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次你要乖乖的留在家里哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.45,0:12:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂你听到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.92,0:12:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.92,0:12:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫做莉露的女孩\N就是驾驶G战影的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再表示的吃惊一点嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.56,0:12:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.39,0:12:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管了，要出击了，快走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战影出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EFA已经开始战斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.20,0:13:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居民的避难措施\N似乎已经完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.76,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇及超重机组各机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将在135秒后进入\N与外星异种作战的空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.47,0:13:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来军方打算无视我们的请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管任何时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人心都是难以推测的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.27,0:14:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司，去引诱外星异种\N让它注意我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.47,0:14:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，让你瞧瞧我训练的成果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去!糟糕了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司，你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是刚刚的那女孩在...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.58,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全超重机组\N进入合神领域了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战骑的诸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.89,0:14:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动合神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.99,0:15:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工学型态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神机超重神合神完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫微洞崩坏加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各机组正常运作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子安定指数98%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次又会进化到什么程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.30,0:16:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重破坏炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有效...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每一发都被弹开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神机超重神被...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒下了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.65,0:17:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个外星异种有着令人难以置信\N的硬度与力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.66,0:17:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人似乎有增强装甲的样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右脚飞弹发射口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.83,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及左上腕部连结部份受损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子安定供给回路发生异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副系统启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离临界点为止5433点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左上腕部连结部份受损...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.38,0:17:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那岂不是无法发射\N超重压力拳了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重压力拳并不只一个喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.65,0:17:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!该不会......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.89,0:17:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右侧重钻机座舱\N超重压力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射预备!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.43,0:17:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要...要由我来发射吗~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,击出!!压力拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.14,0:18:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有效?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.77,0:18:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真...真的很对不起各位...\N都是我能力不够......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的错，爱娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙，只能使用剑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.65,0:18:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑身亮现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工学终结!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.72,0:19:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧... 超重剑...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.29,0:19:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然也没有效用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.49,0:19:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.29,0:19:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离临界点为止1922点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!用超重弧光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.13,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，\N只会让临界值更加接近而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这...这该怎么办...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用超重新月镖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.61,0:19:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.67,0:19:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是G战影的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.71,0:19:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战影的翅膀是可以当作武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个女孩耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.65,0:19:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一位就是G战影的飞行员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.15,0:19:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是第六位G战骑成员，对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.72,0:19:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.96,0:19:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战影超重新月镖\N发射预备!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重新月镖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.47,0:20:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再向各位作一次介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.91,0:20:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战影的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.78,0:20:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.15,0:20:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘伊露，早上也是得安静的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.52,0:20:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止为我们解危的\N就是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教，莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.15,0:21:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着在烈阳热气下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.40,0:21:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈现形形色色的摆动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.84,0:21:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知该为何这般\N心头思绪纷乱不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.55,0:22:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就这么视而不见\N朝向明日飞去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.02,0:22:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为无法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.19,0:22:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才说出了这么不客气的话语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.63,0:22:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤单一人地强出头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.47,0:22:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换来的只有误解\N矛盾与迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.34,0:22:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于那牵系着悲伤的羁绊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.61,0:22:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让微笑的双眸中渗出了泪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.08,0:22:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想将这暖意传送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.85,0:22:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便紧握着手一直不愿放开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.69,0:22:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让这祈祷得以传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.73,0:22:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐，茶点跟便当都准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.87,0:22:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战骑的诸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.97,0:22:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向莉露的欢迎野餐会前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回播出"没有笑容的少女"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.81,0:23:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下周也会照料各位的和平!